register.text:
let(:user_account) { create(:user_account) } let(:user_session_attributes) do { email: user_account.username, password: user_account.password } end
subject { post :create, params: { user_session: user_session_attributes } }
context "成功する場合" do it "リダイレクトされること" do subject expect(response).to redirect_to users_informations_path end end
context "失敗する場合" do before do user_session_attributes[:password] = "#{user_session_attributes[:password]}hogehoge" end
it { expect(subject).to render_template :new } end
